      <hedline>
        <hl1>Desperate Passage</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Virginia Ravenscroft-Scott letter on June 18 article holds it is perverse to put two well-off American reporters aboard Haitian refugee boat7</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The idea of putting two well-off Americans on board a boat full of Haitian refugees to see what it's like was perverse. These reporters, with money and homes and rescue in the wings, could not possibly share the true horror of the experience.</p>
        <p>Virginia Ravenscroft-Scott  Brooklyn</p>
      </block>
